snippet.title: Trails of Cold Steel III - Trial By Fire - Gameplay Trailer (PS4)
snippet.description:
Learn more @ thelegendofheroes.com

As powerful new enemies rise up, Rean and his allies must draw upon all of their skills, strengths, and strategies in order to defeat them. The students of Class VII may be unproven in the field of battle, but they will need to learn fast and act fast in order to survive!

Available September 24, 2019 for PlayStation 4.
